author: MBlazier620
title: Too Many Stickers
review: This set is pretty good, the only thing i think to be wrong. I felt that there were too many stickers. In fact there were two full sheets of stickers, some of them where so small that they required me to use tweezers. I have to say those stickers ruined the building experience for me.

author: Ribird
title: New Boat Designs.
review: Great new boat designs. Yes there were too many stickers, but the finished look was great!
